# Fleet

## Rules

- Keep Agones and cluster runtime resources here.
- Matchmaker consumes fleet allocation APIs but does not own fleet manifests.

## Structure

- `k8s/` — Kubernetes and Agones manifests/helm values.
- `infra/` — fleet-owned infrastructure resources.
- `scripts/` — operational scripts for rollout, validation, diagnostics.
